## System 3: AI Ops Event Bus (MUST FOLLOW)

Structured communication channel between orchestration layer and code agents.

### Session Start Obligations

1. Scan `.ops/needs-code-fix/` -- if files exist, analyze and create fix plan
2. Check `.ops/state/active-incidents.json` -- understand ongoing incident context

### Post-Fix Obligations

1. Write `.ops/completed/INC-{timestamp}.json` (root_cause + fix + prevention)
2. Create runbook: `docs/runbooks/{issue-slug}.md` (enables auto-response next time)
3. Implement recurrence prevention: add hooks/tests/monitoring rules

### .ops/ Directory Convention

| Directory | Write | Read | Purpose |
|-----------|-------|------|---------|
| `state/` | Both | Both | Real-time system/business state |
| `needs-code-fix/` | Orchestrator | Agent | Incidents requiring code fixes |
| `completed/` | Agent | Orchestrator | Fix completion + learning data |
| `auto-resolved/` | Orchestrator | Both | Self-resolved incident records |
| `reports/` | Orchestrator | Both | Daily/weekly/monthly reports |

All files are JSON. Incident ID format: `INC-YYYY-MMDD-NNN`

