## Commit Format

```
type: description (English, lowercase, present tense)

Types:
  feat      New feature
  fix       Bug fix
  refactor  Code improvement (no behavior change)
  docs      Documentation only
  style     Formatting (no code change)
  test      Add/update tests
  chore     Build, config, dependencies

Examples:
  feat: add order cancellation with 2-week notice
  fix: prevent double booking on same time slot
  refactor: extract payment calculation to shared util
```

### Branch Names: type/business-concept

```
feat/order-processing
feat/payment-onboarding
fix/double-booking-prevention
```

