## Security Rules (Always Active)

- Row-level security enabled on every database table (if supported)
- Server-side validation on all API routes
- Webhook signatures always verified
- No hardcoded secrets -- use environment variables
- Session stored in HTTP-only cookies (not localStorage)
- Run docs/manuals/security/checklist.md after every task

