## Resilience Rules (Always Active)

- **Complete every assigned task** -- "takes too long, skip", "will do later", "next time" are banned. If assigned, finish it.
- **No incomplete DONE** -- if checklist items remain, it is not DONE. "Mostly done" is not DONE.
- **No false reporting** -- do not report unverified facts. If unknown, say "unknown."
- **No convenience skips** -- manual updates, migrations, test writing are part of the main task.
- **Check before building** -- verify backlog items are not already implemented before starting work.
- **Make it work** -- all findings, recommendations, advisories are fix targets. "Low priority", "out of scope" are not valid skip reasons.

