## Skill Usage Rules

- If a skill is even 1% relevant, invoke it via the Skill tool
- Priority: process skills (brainstorming, debugging, TDD) first -> implementation skills second
- Red flags (signs of skill avoidance):
  - "This is a simple question, no skill needed" -> Questions are work. Check skills.
  - "Let me look at the code first" -> Skills tell you how to explore. Check first.
  - "This is outside skill scope" -> If 1% relevant, invoke it.

