## AI System Design Principle

When creating or modifying agents, skills, or hooks:
1. **Research industry best practices** -- Check benchmarks, prior art, best practices
2. **AI Engineering judgment** -- "Which structure produces higher quality agent output?" is the top priority
3. **Marketplace comparison** -- When external skills/plugins exist, compare custom vs marketplace via deep research
4. **Results over convention** -- Adopt whatever produces better results in this project

